{"tid":2375412,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"兩大禍港源頭，其中臭痢狗已經收撚左皮，淨番最後一個","createTime":"2021-01-22T04:28:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T13:32:06.000Z","uid":70819,"like":28,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"62abffdd8a0902f918e15584add1b35a9c988229","tid":2375412,"uid":70819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T04:28:43.000Z","msg":"自從痢狗前年攞完歐聯<br />\n香港就冇好過<br />\n而家痢狗收埋皮<br />\n得返最後一個禍港源頭<br />\n就係<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>般奴</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n般奴上年1月29號宣布成為死獌狗<br />\n第二日香港就有首宗本地武肺個案<br />\n仲一路爆到而家<br />\n般奴一日唔收皮<br />\n香港都唔會回復正常<br />\n幾時斷腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"115bbfb7255f7b9392c86c39d9d50f24381a1828","tid":2375412,"uid":160592,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T04:32:41.000Z","msg":"唔好影衰波台啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1861cfc9862c4223054188557f87a3b0d98f5e83","tid":2375412,"uid":70819,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"115bbfb7255f7b9392c86c39d9d50f24381a1828","tid":2375412,"uid":160592,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T04:32:41.000Z","msg":"唔好影衰波台啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T04:43:36.000Z","msg":"此後，於1月24日年三十晚上增至5宗輸入個案，當中4宗都是乘高鐵返港，進一步突顯高鐵是防疫缺口，<span class=\"red\">在1月30日及2月2日出現兩宗可能本地個案</span>，再於2月4日首次出現三宗本地個案，病毒正式在香港落地生根。"},{"pid":"c24c618fac7388ee7e468b5e2fdac945a79f7341","tid":2375412,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T05:01:29.000Z","msg":"要搵馬高斯亞朗素車死條仆街般奴"},{"pid":"f6a2252a8e21a070f22f3bb136a7327e049d8b19","tid":2375412,"uid":70819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c24c618fac7388ee7e468b5e2fdac945a79f7341","tid":2375412,"uid":5649,"like":2,"disl